    ⟪w, S⟫ ≤ Finset.max' (V.image (⟪w, ·⟫)) (by simp [Finset.image_nonempty]; exact Vne) := by
  exact finset_hull_linear_max Vne S hs (InnerProductSpace.toDual ℝ (E n) w |>.toLinearMap)
```
This lemma is also correct. It shows `inner w S ≤ (V.image (inner w ·)).max' ...`.

So the issue is not with `hull_scalar_prod`, but with `partials_helper2`.

The statement of `partials_helper2` is incorrect. Therefore, it cannot be proven.

